+# Sai Patch
+
+This is a minimal vendored patch of `cosmwasm-crypto` 1.5.11.
+
+The only dependency change is:
+
+- `ed25519-zebra = "3"` -> `ed25519-zebra = { version = "=4.0.3", default-features = false }`
+
+This keeps the CosmWasm 1.5.11 API in place while resolving
+`RUSTSEC-2024-0344`, which is reported through `curve25519-dalek` 3.2.0 in the
+host-only `cosmwasm-std` crypto path. `ed25519-zebra` 4.0.3 resolves
+`curve25519-dalek` to 4.1.3 under its `< 4.2` dependency range.
+
+Remove this patch when the workspace migrates to a Nibiru/CosmWasm release that
+ships the fixed crypto dependency directly.
